00:16:26.260 --> 00:16:28.235 align:middle line:84%
If you see how we
develop neurologically,

00:16:28.235 --> 00:16:30.500 align:middle line:84%
it comes a lot of times
from that connection

00:16:30.500 --> 00:16:33.890 align:middle line:84%
