00:16:48.260 --> 00:16:57.582 align:middle line:84%
Complexity, nutrition, movement,
nurturing, and community.

00:16:57.582 --> 00:16:59.540 align:middle line:84%
>> And we don't have
community in the same way.

00:16:59.540 --> 00:17:01.680 align:middle line:84%
We don't have extended
family in the same way.

00:17:01.680 --> 00:17:05.300 align:middle line:84%
So what is happening
to us physiologically?

00:17:05.300 --> 00:17:07.970 align:middle line:84%
I mean, we can go on all
levels, but since we're

00:17:07.970 --> 00:17:11.599 align:middle line:84%
