00:17:15.119 --> 00:17:16.860 align:middle line:84%
to our parents,
our grandparents?

00:17:16.860 --> 00:17:17.660 align:middle line:90%
What's happening?

00:17:17.660 --> 00:17:18.701 align:middle line:90%
What do you see en masse?

00:17:18.701 --> 00:17:22.390 align:middle line:84%
>> En masse lack of oxytocin,
which is what gives us

00:17:22.390 --> 00:17:25.260 align:middle line:84%
