her children in lactation.

00:17:33.290 --> 00:17:34.970 align:middle line:84%
And what we get
instead, which is

00:17:34.970 --> 00:17:39.140 align:middle line:84%
interesting from an biologically
evolutionary standpoint,

00:17:39.140 --> 00:17:42.192 align:middle line:84%
we get a lot more vasopressin,
which is only two molecules

00:17:42.192 --> 00:17:43.775 align:middle line:84%
difference, which
is quite incredible.

00:17:43.775 --> 00:17:46.655 align:middle line:84%
>> What is the is the difference
