00:17:49.850 --> 00:17:50.870 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh interesting.

00:17:50.870 --> 00:17:53.120 align:middle line:84%
Which makes perfect sense
if you don't have the other.

00:17:53.120 --> 00:17:53.600 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:17:53.600 --> 00:17:56.058 align:middle line:84%
>> I mean, oxytocin has to be
present just to get the child

00:17:56.058 --> 00:17:57.360 align:middle line:90%
